==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Misdoubt
<hw>Mis*doubt"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To be
suspicious of; to have suspicion.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I do not <qex>misdoubt</qex> my wife.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misdoubt</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misdoubt
<hw>Mis*doubt"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Suspicion.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Irresolution; hesitation.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misdoubtful</ent>⟦br⟧
